NOTE 16.  GENERAL EMPLOYEES' STOCK PURCHASE PLAN

IN MAY 1997, SHAREHOLDERS APPROVED 15 MILLION SHARES FOR ISSUANCE UNDER THE

COMPANY'S GENERAL EMPLOYEES' STOCK PURCHASE PLAN (GESPP). SUBSTANTIALLY ALL

EMPLOYEES ARE ELIGIBLE TO PARTICIPATE IN THE PLAN.  PARTICIPANTS ARE GRANTED

OPTIONS AT 85 PERCENT OF MARKET VALUE AT THE DATE OF GRANT.  THERE ARE NO GESPP

SHARES UNDER OPTION AT THE BEGINNING OR END OF EACH YEAR BECAUSE OPTIONS ARE

GRANTED ON THE FIRST BUSINESS DAY AND EXERCISED ON THE LAST BUSINESS DAY OF THE

SAME MONTH.

